comment: Ajinca (NOP) sets the screen on Tucker (PHO) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Cunningham (NOP) establishes a legal guarding position and Morris (PHO) initiates the contact as he cuts along the baseline.
Morris (PHO) sets the screen on Cole (NOP) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
L-Slash shows that Bledsoe (PHO) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot prior to jumping on the field goal attempt, then jumps and releases the ball before returning his pivot to the floor.
Evans (NOP) makes incidental contact that does not affect Morris' (PHO) RSBQ.
Morris (PHO) does not extend his arm into Cunningham (NOP) as he creates space on the step back jump shot.
Pondexter (NOP) turns sideways while setting the screen on Tucker (PHO) and does not give him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Ajinca (NOP) sets the back screen on Morris (PHO) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Morris (PHO) does not affect Evans' (NOP) RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Evans (NOP) ends his dribble on his right foot, then goes left, right, left for a total of 3 steps.
RHH shows Bledsoe (PHO) grab Ajinca's (NOP) left arm, preventing him from securing the rebound.
Evans (NOP) commits a take foul on Tucker (PHO).
